{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_mostma_set_1", "eventName": "高樓之上", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "高樓之上", "storyInfo": "今天的能天使也一如既往地以她的方式進行著送貨。而她所不知道的是，在不遠處的屋頂，有一個人正在看著她。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_lmstreet_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_103_angel_1#8"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  啊哈，讓我看看，五個，不對，六個嗎，來吧，我趕時間，你們一起上吧！", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "char_103_angel_1#8"}, {"id": 10, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "龍門的巷子中，今天的能天使也一如既往地以她的方式進行著送貨。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而她所不知道的是，在不遠處的屋頂，有一個人正在看著她。"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_rooftop_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_213_mostma_1#4", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嘖嘖，小樂還是這麼愛玩，槍法也變得越來越好了。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#4"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_213_mostma_1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你也這麼認為吧，看得我都有點懷念我的銃了。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  找羅德島定製一把銃型法杖？還是算了......要是讓蕾繆安看到可要笑話我了。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_213_mostma_1#3"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  而且那不是會搞得我好像很懷念過去一樣嗎？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#3"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_213_mostma_1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗯？我不怎麼懷念。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_213_mostma_1#5"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  只不過，不懷念，不代表忘記。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#5"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  時過境遷，物是人非，我以為你會對這一點有更深的感觸。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#5"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_213_mostma_1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......也對，你們的感受性和我們並不相同。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我有時候也很好奇，以百年為單位的變遷究竟是怎樣的感覺？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  是不是細微的感情會變得毫無意義？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_213_mostma_1#3"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你知道的，我向來沒什麼所謂。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#3"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  啊，果然是莫斯提馬。", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_213_mostma_1#4"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  伊斯？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#4"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  中午好。", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  大帝有事找我？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  並沒有。最近沒有什麼大事，我也只是路過，然後感到了熟悉的氣息就過來看一看。", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那邊的是......能天使？原來如此，例行公事嗎。", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  沒錯。順便和這傢伙透透氣，聊聊天。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#3"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  啊，那可真是愜意，令人羡慕。", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你呢？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  一如既往，閒不下來。", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你也是辛苦了。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  哪裡哪裡，天生勞碌命罷了。", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  對了，既然正好遇到你，麻煩你一件事。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  請說。", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這傢伙最近跟我抱怨了很多次，或許是鎖的零件出了點問題，可能要麻煩你幫我看一下。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  啊，安魂夜你交給我保管的時候我就覺得鎖有些古舊了，說不定會有些小問題。", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  交給我吧，小事一樁。", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  另一把不需要嗎？", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不用了，畢竟它在鎖裡，另一把只是鑰匙，不會煩我。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing2", "volume": 0.1}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫斯提馬拍了拍腰間的灰色法杖，然後將棕色法杖抽出，遞給了伊斯。"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  老朋友，又見面了。", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......哦，看來它確實心情不是很好，並不想理會我。", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  常有的事。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  說起來，莫斯提馬，之前我一直沒有問，不過，我可以好奇一下，這對鎖與鑰匙你是在哪裡獲得的嗎？", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  它在來到我手上之前，一直在卡茲戴爾附近。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  卡茲戴爾附近......原來如此。", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  沒想到會在那一帶。", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  具體的嘛，雖然我覺得告訴你也沒關係，不過解釋起來會很麻煩，所以還是算了。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  解釋......是對那位黎博利小姐嗎？", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  沒錯，你見過她了？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  之前安魂夜的時候見過一面。", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  很麻煩的女人對吧？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#3"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗯——", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.7, "r": 0.95, "g": 0.95, "b": 0.95, "fadetime": 0.02, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#3"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_atk_arrow_h"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.95, "g": 0.95, "b": 0.95, "fadetime": 0.25, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.6, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 8.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“嘣！”忽然之間，一根弩箭扎在莫斯提馬和伊斯身前的不遠處。"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  看吧。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#2"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  看來我並不受這位小姐歡迎。", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不，她只是在朝我發火而已，還有別的問題嗎？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  仔細想想，雖然我是因為你和大帝才加入企鵝物流，不過在加入之後，我們很少好好聊過。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  有關它的問題，你可以隨時問我。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......你有想過去找它的另外幾片碎片嗎？", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  它現在只剩下這一份碎片了。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  而且就算有，它不是很感興趣，我更不感興趣，就像現在這樣就好。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你知道的，如果它真的不想，從一開始就不會變成這樣。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  原來如此，確實是這個道理。", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我們這樣的存在，有不少都是做出了這樣的選擇。", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  其實我也問過它，有沒有想過出來。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  讓我想想，對了，是在羅德島的幹員測試的時候。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......為什麼？", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗯......因為我覺得那個組織很有意思，所以久違地想要展現一下自己？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#3"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  也有可能是想要嚇一嚇博士。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#3"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不過最後它放棄了，好像是感覺到了什麼。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  哎，不得不說，羅德島確實是個有趣的組織，伊斯你有空了也可以去看一看。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#2"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  等我有空的話，我會的。", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你什麼時候有空？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  誰知道呢，大帝哪天心情不好的時候，我可能就有空了。", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不過，人與人之間的際遇確實足夠奇妙。", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  它在沉眠之後，會遇到與它如此契合的持有者。", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  或許吧。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  雖然要我說的話，這傢伙給我帶來的麻煩，要遠比力量多。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  但你不在乎，不是嗎？", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  確實。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那麼，今天就聊到這裡吧。", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  杖沒問題了我會通知你。", "name": "伊斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_035"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_035", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  好，拜拜。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_213_mostma_1#2"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  火氣這麼大？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#2"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1#3", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  拜你所賜。", "name": "苦難陳述者"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1#3"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1#3", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不勝榮幸。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#3"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1#2", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這個人究竟是什麼人物，我只知道大帝了不得，從不知道企鵝物流裡還有這樣的人物。", "name": "苦難陳述者"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1#2"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你居然會把杖交給他，而且他好像很熟悉這些的樣子。", "name": "苦難陳述者"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1#2"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1#2", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  他是可以說這些的人。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1#3", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  如果不能信任，剛才就不是一發弩箭的事了。", "name": "苦難陳述者"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1#3"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1#3", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你想知道嗎？我可以告訴你。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#3"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1#2", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......免了。老傢伙們明顯也知道，但是沒有告訴我。", "name": "苦難陳述者"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1#2"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這也就意味著，我不應該從你口中得知。", "name": "苦難陳述者"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你這樣不累嗎？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我的職責只是監視你，除此之外，我不關心。", "name": "苦難陳述者"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  真的嗎？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#4"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1#2", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "苦難陳述者"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1#2"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1#2", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  唉，所以說，誰讓你當年自告奮勇接下監視我的任務，很多事沒法知道，還要跟著我跑東跑西，給自己找罪受。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  明知故問。", "name": "苦難陳述者"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我說過，卡茲戴爾那件事你不需要負任何責任。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#5"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那並不是你在場就能讓我不用扣下扳機的情況。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#5"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  而你也不在乎變成現在這樣，對吧？", "name": "苦難陳述者"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  沒錯，你也變得越來越瞭解我了。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#5"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我自己選的，不用你來操心。", "name": "苦難陳述者"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  好吧好吧——對了，昨天公證所的人來了吧，有新的任務？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#2"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  暫時沒有，例行報告而已。不過......", "name": "苦難陳述者"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗯？難道你的職位又變了？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1#2", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  沒錯......唉。", "name": "苦難陳述者？"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1#2"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1#2", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這麼不開心，說出來讓我開心一下。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#3"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1#3", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......獨臂電鋸俠。", "name": "苦難陳述者？"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1#3"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1#3", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗯......他們剛看了龍門產的爛片？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#2"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1#2", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我帶回去的。嘖，早知道給他們帶點藝術電影回去。", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1#2"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1#2", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  哈，哈，哈，然後你下一次就會叫銃與玫瑰。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#3"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  至少比獨臂電鋸俠好。", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.1, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  好了，走吧。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我還以為你打算跟著她一天。", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我看起來有那麼無聊嗎？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我個人認為，在這片大地上，比你無聊的人不會很多。", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我的評價有這麼高？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#4"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我沒在誇你。", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我覺得你在誇我就行了。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#3"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不過，我確實沒那個打算，只是慣例來看一眼，我又不是第一天這麼做了，你也不是不知道。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我知道。你不主動和她接觸對我來說是一件好事，但......", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  自從上次安魂夜我和她聊了幾句後，你好像一直在擔心這個問題。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你還是擔心我會和她接觸，告訴她一些什麼？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  如果你有這個想法，我可能攔不住你，所以我必須瞭解你在這件事上的想法。", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗯......好吧。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  看你的眼神，今天要是不告訴你，你是不打算讓我離開了。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你知道就好。", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  對付你，來硬的要比講道理有用。", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......你認為，讓一個人真的不在乎你的方法是什麼？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  消失在這個人的生活裡。", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不，不夠，如果你出現過，你就無法完全消失。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#5"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你要等到這個人找到新的生活，新的環境。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#5"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  老實說，一開始我也沒想到她會從拉特蘭跑到這裡來。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  大帝告訴我她也加入了企鵝物流的時候，我還是相當吃驚的。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  但你也知道，我從那時候起，直到安魂夜，都沒有和她見過面。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  安魂夜那一次嘛......算是狂歡的一部分吧。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#2"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  她不會就此放棄找你。", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  但她實際上並沒有在找我。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那件事與她沒有直接的聯繫，而我們都不得不對此緘口不言。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我能告訴她嗎，告訴我，獨臂電鋸俠。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1#2", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  求你不要一本正經地喊這個名字。", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1#2"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  很遺憾，這是最高機密，你不能告訴她。", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你看，她最想知道的事情我無法告訴她，那我出現在她面前幹什麼呢？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  和她說一些不痛不癢的話，勾起她的好奇心，把她捲進這邊的事情？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你希望她不在乎你？", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  難道你不這麼希望？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我說過了，從職責上不希望她繼續關注和你有關的事，作為我個人，我不是很在乎。", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  實際上，如果你問我希不希望，我不會說我希望。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  但我輕易地割捨掉了我與拉特蘭的關聯，就好像我當時毫不猶豫地舉起我的銃。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我只能說，如果事情發生了，那就讓它發生吧。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你確實是這樣的人，我也是不喜歡你這一點，你總是不在乎失去。", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  很多人都不喜歡我這一點。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  但我反而很好奇，在乎失去又能怎麼樣呢？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你為你失去的東西和預見到將會失去的東西痛哭流涕，那然後呢？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我不打算和你討論哲學話題。只是既然你這麼想，那為什麼還要這樣來看她？", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你猜？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#2"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  猜不出，我想你不至於無聊到抱著被她發現的想法在做這樣的事。", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你不會是剛看了什麼地攤言情小說吧，少看點。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1#3", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你......！", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1#3"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1#3", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  對了，蕾繆安有沒有和你說過，為什麼明明她不是親生的，小樂的名字，蕾繆樂卻是按照她的名字起的？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  她在工作時不怎麼提她的家庭。", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  也是。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  其實很簡單，在她來到那個家庭時，小樂還沒出生，而為了讓她融入這個家庭，她們的父母選擇了這麼做。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  雖然以她們父母不輸給小樂的歡樂程度，你說是因為懶得想名字所以這麼去取了我覺得也是有可能的。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  總之呢，蕾繆安雖然嘴上不說，心裡對於父母是非常感激的。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  而對於蕾繆樂這個妹妹，她更是打心眼裡愛護。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這和你現在在做的事有什麼關係？", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1#3", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我是這麼想的，獨臂電鋸俠。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  蕾繆安會同意蕾繆樂離開拉特蘭，並不只是因為小樂她說想要來找我。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1#3", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  她是分得清的人，如果這件事真的對小樂來說變成了某種執念，我不覺得她會放行。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#5"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  恰恰是因為那件事與小樂沒有什麼關聯，對小樂來說尋找我並不是無法放棄的執念——", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#5"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  她才會能夠來到龍門，並且加入企鵝物流。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#5"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1#3", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  蕾繆安真正希望的，其實是小樂能夠出來闖一闖，找到自己的生活。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  而她將照看小樂的職責，間接地交給了我。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  明明你不辭而別？", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  正因我不辭而別。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  遠遠地看一看可算不上照顧。", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我並沒有因為她的到來而離開企鵝物流，本來我應該這麼做的，不是嗎？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1#3", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1#3"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  所以你是覺得蕾繆安希望你這麼做，你才會這麼去做？", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1#3"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1#3", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  誰知道呢。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#2"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  也有可能只是我給自己找了一個這麼做的理由。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#2"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  真意外，你竟然會為自己找了這樣一個感性的理由。", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我只是對許多事情沒有那麼有所謂，又不是絕情。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  負罪感，懷念，悲傷，等等等等。這些情感都曾在我心裡浮現，只是被我漸漸磨平。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  要是被你或者蕾繆安說絕交之類的話，我也會難過的。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  難過多久？", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不知道，一個星期還是會有的吧？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1#3"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  倒是夠久。", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  退一萬步說，我也算和她們姐妹一起長大，小樂來到我這邊，稍微照拂一二也是人之常情吧。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  所以，你打算就一直這麼下去？", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  差不多？她和她現在的夥伴相處得已經很好了。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我想，我們會在某些地方偶遇的，但也只是偶遇而已，這樣你該放心了吧。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  確實——", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  雖然我想這麼說，但是從我個人角度出發，這對她並不公平，即使我沒有資格這麼說。", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  或許吧。但一切從我成為鎖與匙的主人起，就不再有公平可言。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  如果有什麼事情需要我和她接觸，我不會避諱，如果有些話不得不由我告訴她，我會親口告訴她。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  而現實則是——並沒有這樣的需求。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我有我的任務，而這孩子也在這座城市找到了新的生活。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你不覺得這在某種意義上其實很公平嗎？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......你覺得這樣行就行。", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_213_mostma_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  好了，走吧。等到哪天她倒了大霉被捲進我們這邊的事，再繼續討論這個話題吧。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 300.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1", "name2": "char_empty", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_300_phenxi_1#3"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我不會讓這種事發生的。", "name": "獨臂電鋸俠"}, "figure_art": "char_300_phenxi_1#3"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_213_mostma_1"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  但願如此。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "char_213_mostma_1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}